'''雲生·達保羅·佩里卡'''（{{lang-fr|'''Vincent de Paul Péricard'''}}，{{bd|1982年|10月3日|catIdx=Pericard, Vincent}}）出生於[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]，是一名[[法國|法國]][[職業|職業]]職業足球員，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[英格蘭足球議會南部聯賽|英格蘭足球議會南部聯賽]]球會[[哈雲特與禾達路維足球會|哈雲特]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
;早年
在[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]出生的佩里卡自小移居[[法國|法國]]，於[[法甲|法甲]]老牌球會[[圣艾蒂安足球俱乐部|聖伊天]]出道，未幾於代表法國U18作賽時被[[意甲|意甲]]勁旅[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|祖雲達斯]]相中羅致旗下。在[[都靈|都靈]]兩年僅於2002年3月20日在[[歐聯|歐聯]]無關痛癢的第二輪分組賽最後一場主場一次代表「老婦人」出戰[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，於下半場後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/history/season=2001/round=1546/match=1018357/report=rp.html |title=Torment for Arsenal in Turin |publisher=[[UEFA|''uefa.com'']] |date=2002-03-20 |accessdate=2009-12-30}}</ref>，但卻獲得時任[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英甲]]球會[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]領隊的[[哈里·雷德克纳普|哈里·雷德克纳普]]賞識。

;樸茨茅夫
2002年夏季佩里卡以借用身份加盟[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]一個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Trio in, three on way |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2238511,00.html |publisher=skysports.com |date=2002-06-05 |accessdate=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2016-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605121352/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2238511,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於2002/03年球季揭幕戰主場對[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]處子登場，開賽僅8分鐘的勁射對方門將僅能擋出，隊友[[Deon_Burton|-{zh-hans:迪恩·伯頓; zh-hk:迪恩·貝頓;}-]]（Deon Burton）門前「執死雞」先拔頭籌；下半場開場佩里卡接應[[加利·奧尼爾|-{zh-hans:加里·奥尼尔; zh-hk:加利·奧尼爾;}-]]（Gary O'Neil）傳球頂入為球隊鎖定2-0勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2181122.stm |title=Portsmouth 2-0 N Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-08-10 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2020-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129023239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2181122.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然下半季佩里卡飽受傷患困擾<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Pompey lose Pericard for a month |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2251747,00.html |publisher=skysports.com |date=2002-12-02 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143353/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2251747,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Pompey lose Pericard |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2262058,00.html |publisher=skysports.com |date=2003-04-03 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143355/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2262058,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但整季仍為樸茨茅夫上陣35場及射入10球，其中9個為聯賽入球，協助球隊贏得甲組聯賽冠軍及升班[[英超|英超]]資格。球季結束後樸茨茅夫向祖雲達斯要求正式收購佩里卡<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Pericard fancies Pompey stay |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2267920,00.html |publisher=skysports.com |date=2003-06-10 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042029/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2267920,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，祖雲達斯開價100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，最終樸茨茅夫還價44萬英鎊附加33%轉售分紅取得佩里卡的擁有權<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Pompey agree Pericard price |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2271306,00.html |publisher=skysports.com |date=2003-07-21 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143402/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2271306,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2003年至2004年英格蘭超級聯賽|2003/04年球季]]季初佩里卡一直擔任球隊正選，直到9月尾因大腿肌肉撕裂而缺陣。12月才告復健重返一隊，但在復出前為預備隊上陣卻重創十字韌帶，因傷而提早「收咧」。2004年夏季他返回[[法國|法國]]動[[手術|手術]]治理傷患，手術後花了[[2004年至2005年英格蘭超級聯賽|整季]]用於康復治療。2005年8月傷勢復原後，他前赴[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]參加為[[友誼賽|友賽]]一支法國業餘球隊維勒蒙伯（Villemomble）的[[喀麥隆國家足球隊|國家隊]]訓練營。

[[2005年至2006年英格蘭超級聯賽|2003/04年球季]]佩里卡重返[[法頓公園球場|法頓公園球場]]，獲外借到[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]3個月爭取回復狀態<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Striker Pericard loaned to Blades |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/4246828.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-09-14 |accessdate=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2005-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051213211656/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/4246828.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間在對[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]及[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]各射入1球<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4344632.stm |title=Millwall 0-4 Sheff Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=18 October 2005 |accessdate=24 October 2009 |archive-date=2005-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051219013335/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4344632.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4387916.stm |title=Sheff Utd 4-0 Luton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=1 November 2005 |accessdate=24 October 2009 |archive-date=2005-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051105083922/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4387916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；其後於2006年2月再被外借到[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]渡過餘下球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Argyle bring in Pericard on loan |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/plymouth_argyle/4700316.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-02-10 |accessdate=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2006-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060304201159/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/plymouth_argyle/4700316.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2月18日主場3-1擊敗[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]包辦3個入球，首次在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]上演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Plymouth 3-1 Coventry |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4703646.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-02-18 |accessdate=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2008-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080315150409/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4703646.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於5月在尚餘1場聯賽獲召提早歸隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/4969302.stm |title=Pompey recall Pericard from loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-03 |accessdate=2010-01-04 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307065253/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/4969302.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，季後約滿遭樸茨茅夫放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2377182,00.html |title=Primus signs Pompey deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-05-18 |accessdate=2010-01-04 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309161542/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2377182,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;史篤城
由[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]轉投[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]的領隊[[東尼·佩利斯|東尼·佩利斯]]隨即向佩里卡招手<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2380608,00.html |title=Pericard set for Stoke move |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-06-17 |accessdate=2010-01-04 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010849/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2380608,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於2006年6月19日以自由身加盟史篤城，動筆簽約3年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Striker Pericard signs for Stoke |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5095918.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-06-19 |accessdate=2007-08-25 |archive-date=2008-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080315180400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5095918.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是東尼·佩利斯重返史篤城第二度任教首名簽入的球員。最初他的表現出色，於開季首場主場對升班競爭對手[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]先拔頭籌，射入加盟後首個入球，協助球隊2-0獲勝<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/5248144.stm |title=Stoke 2-0 Derby |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=8 August 2006 |accessdate=24 October 2009}}</ref>，繼後於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|達寧頓]]再下一城<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/5266386.stm |title=Stoke 1-2 Darlington |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=22 August 2006 |accessdate=24 October 2009}}</ref>及返回聯賽在對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]又入一球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6050698.stm |title=Stoke 2-1 Sunderland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=17 October 2006 |accessdate=24 October 2009 |archive-date=2006-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061108124014/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6050698.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在餘下球季他卻無以為繼，更被另一名由樸茨茅夫來投的[[里卡多·弗勒|富拿]]（Ricardo Fuller）取代其正前鋒席位。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]佩里卡參加史篤城的季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]並且取得入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6900841.stm |title=Stoke start pre-season with win |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-07-16 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6900841.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6915236.stm |title=Bad Aussee 1-2 Stoke City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-07-25 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310122427/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6915236.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，在新球季剛展開還未有上陣機會，佩里卡於2007年8月24日以[[妨礙司法公正|妨礙司法公正]]罪被普利茅夫刑事法庭（Plymouth Crown Court）判處入獄4個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Speeding striker jailed for lying |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/staffordshire/6962376.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2007-08-24 |accessdate=2007-08-24 |archive-date=2008-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080315051830/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/staffordshire/6962376.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，案情透露去年3月6日，當時佩里卡以外借身份效力[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]，駕駛其[[梅賽德斯-賓士|梅賽德斯-賓士]]CLK 500轎跑車由[[朴茨茅斯|朴茨茅斯]]前往[[普利茅斯|普利茅斯]]進行訓練，在A38公路一處雙程雙向分隔車道（dual carriageway）以時速103[[公里|公里]]被映超速相，曾有兩次超速被停牌紀錄的佩里卡聲稱當時是其後父駕車，當警方在[[法國|法國]]找到其後父時，發現他自2003年後再沒有踏足[[英國|英國]]，而其中一張正面超速相證實佩里卡當時是司機，警方多次發信給他不獲回覆，直到12月佩里卡才向警方發表聲名認錯及道歉，但其後被捕及提出控訴。在服刑1個月後，於9月24日獲釋，但需要配帶電子標籤，每天只可由早上7時至晚上7時離家12小時，史篤城需要將晚練時間表備案讓他可以超時回家<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2743198,00.html |title=Jailed striker to return |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-09-20 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080110/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2743198,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，佩里卡於10月初返回史篤城復操，表示監獄食物差，經常肚餓及體重下降<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2776741,00.html |title=Pericard relishing return |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-10-03 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085410/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2776741,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但因繫於足踝的電子標籤在操練及為預備隊上陣時曾經鬆脫，他於10月11日再次被捕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2797780,00.html |title=Stoke's Pericard re-arrested |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-10-12 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085435/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2797780,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於10月24日再次獲釋<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Stoke star Pericard leaves prison |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7061898.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-25 |accessdate=2008-01-25 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306071946/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7061898.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨即於週末正選出戰[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7054121.stm |title=Bristol City 1-0 Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-27 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307032410/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7054121.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他在史篤城陣中已非必然正選，直到2008年3月僅為球隊在5場聯賽及1場[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]上陣，沒有入球，於3月14日被外借到另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/7296982.stm |title=Pericard makes Southampton move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-14 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118160330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/7296982.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣5場亦沒有斬獲，季後結束借用返回史篤城，而球隊已取得聯賽亞軍及直接升班[[英超|英超]]席位，但佩里卡在史篤城這個重要球季可說是毫無貢獻。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]佩里卡只獲派在盃賽上陣，於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]分別出戰[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]、[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]及[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]，在對雷丁時除先拔頭籌外，更於[[加時賽|加時]]後雙方仍然2-2和局，[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]時為史篤城射入最後一球，以4-3淘汰對手<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7626760.stm |title=Stoke 2-2 Reading (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-23 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801095812/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7626760.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後佩里卡表示他已重新做人<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_4189875,00.html |title=Pericard - I'm a changed man |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-09-24 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309124700/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_4189875,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，將於季後約滿的佩里卡希望憑表現獲得續約機會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4194926,00.html |title=Pericard pursues Potters deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-09-25 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135417/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4194926,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。直到2008年12月13日他才獲派為球隊首次在[[英超|英超]]上陣，於主場0-0賽和[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]下半場後補登場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7763489.stm |title=Stoke 0-0 Fulham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-13 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |archive-date=2016-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920055916/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7763489.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；一星期後作客對剛由[[萨姆·阿勒代斯|艾拿戴斯]]接手領軍的[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]更正選上陣，雖然12月份取得4次聯賽上陣，當球隊在1月轉會窗引入[[占士·比亞堤|比亞堤]]及[[亨利·卡马拉|亨利·卡马拉]]（Henri Camara），他亦已意識到自己為一隊上陣無多，於2009年2月20日毅然以外借身份加盟[[英甲|英甲]]球隊[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]三個月<ref name = "Lions close in on Pericard deal">{{cite news |language=en |title=Lions close in on Pericard deal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7900472.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-20 |accessdate=2009-02-20 |archive-date=2009-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223101327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7900472.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但僅第二場比賽即受傷被擔架抬離場，賽後證實撕裂跟腱需要動[[手術|手術]]，餘下球季亦告「泡湯」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4971163,00.html |title=Pericard suffers injury blow |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-02-05 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010926/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4971163,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7911089.stm |title=Striker Pericard out for season |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-25 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307145029/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7911089.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。球季結束後合約屆滿的佩里卡遭史篤城放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8079486.stm |title=Stoke offer new contract to Diao |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-02 |accessdate=2010-01-12 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128113104/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8079486.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;卡素爾
遭棄用後佩里卡曾短暫參加[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]、[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]及[[黑池足球會|黑池]]的試訓<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5529910,00.html |title=Johnson opts against duo |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-01 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140745/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5529910,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8179829.stm |title=Pericard joins Cardiff on trial |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-01 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307080904/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8179829.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5547764,00.html |title=Seasiders trials for duo |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-10 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140751/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5547764,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後再到[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]仍然不得要領<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5599939,00.html |title=Blades rule out Pericard deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-10-02 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081049/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5599939,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終於2009年10月13日以短約形式加盟[[英甲|英甲]]的[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]，為期僅三個月至翌年1月屆滿<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/8305168.stm |title=Pericard completes Carlisle move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-13 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2019-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231115000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/8305168.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於10月17日首次披甲作客出戰[[约维尔足球俱乐部|伊奧維]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8295550.stm |title=Yeovil 3-1 Carlisle |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307063910/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8295550.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；於返回主場2-1擊敗[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]即取得加盟後首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en 
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8306770.stm |title=Carlisle 2-1 Southend |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=24 October 2009 |accessdate=2 November 2009}}</ref>。佩里卡在上半季為球隊在各項競賽上陣16場及射入6球，雖然領隊[[格雷格·阿波特|格雷格·阿波特]]（Greg Abbott）希望他能延長合約留效到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5761028,00.html |title=Abbott hopes for Pericard stay |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-12-09 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308011045/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5761028,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他最初表示願意<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5771698,00.html |title=Pericard keen on Carlisle deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-12-14 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140832/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5771698,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於2010年1月12日正式約滿卡素爾的佩里卡最終拒絕留隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/8454246.stm |title=Striker Vincent Pericard rejects Carlisle United deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031073524/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/8454246.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，預計即將轉投另一支[[英甲|英甲]]球隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11732_5832694,00.html |title=Pericard shuns deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-05 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308021833/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11732_5832694,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然有[[英冠|英冠]]球隊對他表示興趣，佩里卡選擇加盟[[英甲|英甲]]的[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]，簽約18個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8460136.stm |title=Swindon complete Vincent Pericard signing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-14 |accessdate=2010-01-15 |archive-date=2019-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231114957/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8460136.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
佩里卡曾代表法國在不同青少年年齡組別參加國際賽，最後為[[法國21歲以下國家足球隊|法國U21]]<ref name = "Lions close in on Pericard deal"/>。擁有[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]及[[法國|法國]]雙重[[國籍|國籍]]的佩里卡亦曾參加[[喀麥隆國家足球隊|喀麥隆國家隊]]的訓練營。

